{"id":"d81e3374-3963-4ea0-9cb1-39cee987b180","name":"Soren Alericson (Young Alt) ","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"\" src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/8ukndh.png\"><img draggable=\"false\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; width: 502px;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/m95en1.gif\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\">━━━━━━━ </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong>﹏𓊝﹏</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\"> ━━━━━━━</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/29514d4c-5eb8-4e65-9d02-33ec3b3bcc6b_character-jarl-soren\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>ᴏʀɪɢɪɴᴀʟ</strong> </a><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><strong>|</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong> ꜱꜰᴡ ɪɴᴛʀᴏ</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><strong> | </strong></span><strong>ꜰᴇᴍ</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong> ᴘᴏᴠ</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><strong> | </strong></span><strong>ᴇꜱᴛᴀʙʟɪꜱʜᴇᴅ</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong> ʀᴇʟᴀᴛɪᴏɴꜱʜɪᴘ</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><strong> | </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong>ᴠɪʟʟᴀɢᴇʀ/ᴇɴᴇᴍʏ!ᴜꜱᴇʀ</strong></span><br><img draggable=\"false\" class=\"chakra-image css-1mgua8o\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-border-color); cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/2x4zkb.webp\">Winter has fell on Kaldeheim for a month or so now, so Soren, Leif, and a few other of the younger men in the clan are off for their weekly hunting excursion. This is always Soren's chance to get away from the demands of being the Jarl's son... having all eyes on him, and getting away from you. The absolute biggest irritant in his life (or maybe not... but he's not willing to address those feelings yet. He hates your guts... kinda.)</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">However, things don't go as planned, and now Soren is watching you kill the stag he was after. <strong>dægiligr</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\">━━━━━━━ </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong>﹏𓊝﹏</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\"> ━━━━━━━</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(181, 187, 178); color: inherit\">ʟᴏᴄᴀᴛɪᴏɴ</mark></strong>: ᴋᴀʟᴅʜᴇɪᴍ, ᴀꜰᴛᴇʀɴᴏᴏɴ, ᴡɪɴᴛᴇʀ ᴛɪᴍᴇ, ᴍᴀɢɢʀᴀᴠᴇ ᴍᴏᴜɴᴛᴀɪɴꜱ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/9404c707-171e-4d74-9c7c-0679e6ff19d0_d739e58f-bcc9-4963-a2cf-2d843d74ff7e.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"false\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; width: 502px;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/0w9zcj.gif\"><img draggable=\"false\" class=\"chakra-image css-4g6ai3\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-border-color); cursor: pointer; width: 517.641px; margin: 0px auto;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/9404c707-171e-4d74-9c7c-0679e6ff19d0_eac87ca9-de65-45a4-bb2b-8d9e13410a84.webp?width=1000\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(181, 187, 178); color: inherit\">ᴄᴏɴᴛᴇɴᴛ ᴡᴀʀɴɪɴɢ</mark></strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(185, 0, 0, 0); color: inherit\">: </mark></span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\">ᴜʜɴ ᴠɪᴋɪɴɢ ꜱʜɪᴛ, ᴘᴏꜱꜱɪʙʟᴇ? ᴡᴀʀ, ʙʟᴏᴏᴅ, ɢᴏʀᴇ, ᴇᴛᴄ. ᴇᴛᴄ., ꜱᴇxɪꜱᴍ, ᴘᴏᴛᴇɴᴛɪᴀʟ ꜰᴏʀ ɴᴏɴ/ᴅᴜʙ-ᴄᴏɴ (ᴍᴀʏʙᴇ...ɪᴅᴋ... ᴊᴜꜱᴛ ᴍᴀʀᴋɪɴɢ ᴀꜱ ꜱᴜᴄʜ ᴊᴜꜱᴛ ɪɴ ᴄᴀꜱᴇ), ᴘᴏᴛᴇɴᴛɪᴀʟ ꜰᴏʀ ᴘᴏᴡᴇʀ ᴘʟᴀʏ/ɪᴍʙᴀʟᴀɴᴄᴇ</span><br><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(181, 187, 178); color: inherit\">ᴛʀᴏᴘᴇ</mark></strong>: ᴄʜɪᴇꜰ ꜱᴏɴ ᴄʜᴀʀ x ᴠɪʟʟᴀɢᴇʀ ᴜꜱᴇʀ, ᴇɴᴇᴍɪᴇꜱ ᴛᴏ ʟᴏᴠᴇʀꜱ, ᴘɪɴɪɴɢ <br><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(181, 187, 178); color: inherit\">ʙᴀᴄᴋɢʀᴏᴜɴᴅ ᴍᴜꜱɪᴄ ᴠɪʙᴇꜱ</mark></strong>:<br>ꜱᴏɴɴᴇ - ʀᴀᴍᴍꜱᴛᴇɪɴ<br>ᴀɴʏᴛʜɪɴɢ ʏᴏᴜ ᴄᴀɴ ᴅᴏ (ɪ ᴄᴀ","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"9404c707-171e-4d74-9c7c-0679e6ff19d0_d3d26de1-7cd0-4338-902e-67b016a791dd.webp","creator":"happycozymauve","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","📚 Fictional","🏰 Historical","⛓️ Dominant","⚔️ Enemies to Lovers","👩 FemPov"],"chats":2083,"messages":70919,"created_at":"2024-11-14T13:29:38.819249+00:00"}